      "class": "Evidence",
      "entity_id": null,
      "paper_id": "paper",
      "text_span_id": "discussion_2",
      "text": "AURKA directly phosphorylates PLK1 at the conserved Thr210 residue within its activation loop, a modification essential for PLK1 activation.",
